{"tid":1491584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個你哋一定要睇，有字幕，拘捕兩萬人之後重有有人敢上街!","createTime":"2019-08-20T13:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T13:54:44.000Z","uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb25d4394050b92fd94c5b540162bd465ccd10d","tid":1491584,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JUzj_cZF0Cw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJUzj_cZF0Cw&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9iWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=d857a99e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JUzj_cZF0Cw</a><br />\n<br />\n中共製造恐怖有兩個方法<br />\n<br />\n1 好似64咁樣殺幾十萬人， 殺到真係冇人敢上嘞！<br />\n<br />\n2 喺西方注視之下，中共唔敢一大量殺害香港人，但佢一定會大量拘捕製造恐怖！<br />\n恐怖到冇一個人敢再上街，呢個數字會係可能超過一萬人！<br />\n<br />\n3 所以香港人一定要計劃，點樣同中國鬥爭落去，點樣攬炒，點樣令到佢唔敢落重手.<br />\n<br />\n估唔到吾爾開希講嘢都好有文路，講得好有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158325e98e844bb11e4d3a98d17d5281986f9ce7","tid":1491584,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"屌佢拉到二三千香港都獨立咗啦屌"},{"pid":"8e6e1bfbffbec0e5e0a8d1b6d0c8ca17300c9acc","tid":1491584,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:09:38.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5d7b4cd623cf56548f32db0d14c987a1af9ba1f","tid":1491584,"uid":271056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"一早知道 8964出席過天安門示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算係對我既啟蒙運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e934132bf61c3fb3d20e14e5f2cb4c990c6a51aa","tid":1491584,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike